videos.headline: Brian Thomas's TD catch gives LSU the early lead
videos.description: Brian Thomas Jr. hauls in a 13-yard touchdown to give LSU the first points of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brian Thomas's TD catch gives LSU the early lead) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU punter pulls off slick fake punt with a jump pass
videos.description: LSU fakes a punt and throws a pass to convert on fourth down against Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LSU punter pulls off slick fake punt with a jump pass) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson Jr. punches in the TD for Bama
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. bruises his way in for a 2-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson Jr. punches in the TD for Bama) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bama INT leads to John Metchie TD just before half
videos.description: Jalyn Armour-Davis picks off Max Johnson, then Bryce Young capitalizes on the turnover with an 8-yard TD pass to John Metchie.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bama INT leads to John Metchie TD just before half) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young drops perfect deep ball to Williams for Bama TD
videos.description: Bryce Young finds Jameson Williams over the middle for the 58-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young drops perfect deep ball to Williams for Bama TD) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jack Bech hauls in a TD as LSU pulls within a score

videos.headline: No. 2 Alabama holds off scare from LSU
videos.description: Bryce Young and Alabama stave off the LSU Tigers with a 20-14 win in Tuscaloosa.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (No. 2 Alabama holds off scare from LSU) 2021/11/6 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Alabama totals six rushing yards, escapes tenacious LSU
videos.description: While totaling only six rushing yards, the No. 2 Crimson Tide escape a fiery night from the Tigers and walk away with a 20-14 victory. (edited)
